## 🛠️ Setup Instructions

### 1. **Create Project Structure**
```bash
mkdir kudarilang
cd kudarilang
mkdir bin lib examples tests

2. Copy All Files

Copy each file content to respective locations
Make sure bin/kudari.js is executable: chmod +x bin/kudari.js

3. Install & Test

npm install
node bin/kudari.js --example    # Create examples
node bin/kudari.js examples/hello.kudari    # Test

4. Global Installation (Optional)

npm install -g .
kudari --help    # Now works from anywhere!

